  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dad\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dad \u0dbd\u0dd9\u0dc3 \u0d8b\u0daf\u0dca\u0db0\u0db8\u0db1\u0dba \u0d89\u0dc4\u0dc5\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Inflation hits record highs",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "According to the Department of Census and Statistics, inflation in Sri Lanka has risen to 60.8 percent in July.",
        "Surface inflation, measured by the annual point change in the National Consumer Price Index, has thus risen.",
        "In July, food inflation rose to 90.9 percent, non-food inflation to 46.5 percent, and transport inflation to 143.6 percent."
      ],
